{"id":193678,"type":1,"name":"忍びよる恋はくせもの","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/e5/dc/193678_V5jvH.jpg","summary":"只为世上唯一的主君效命，义不容辞竭尽全力，\r\n在当时被称为“忍者”的他们，至今还保留那种打扮的几乎所剩无几……\r\n\r\n出身忍者世家的奏誓死效忠主人东城惠吾，随侍在他身旁。\r\n奏得知东城家的世仇丰田咏士也跟惠吾念同一所男校，\r\n便决定要为惠吾除去咏士的性命。\r\n然而假装普通学生进入同所学校就读的奏其实有着一个不为人知的秘密……","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>忍者之恋千万当心</li><li><span>册数: </span>5</li><li><span>话数: </span>24</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/9110\">キリシマソウ</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/19306\">KADOKAWA</a> / <a href=\"/person/1581\">エンターブレイン</a>、<a href=\"/person/7611\">尖端出版</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8586\">comic B's-LOG キュン!</a>→<a href=\"/person/10217\">B's-LOG COMIC</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>忍者之戀千萬當心</li><li><span>发售日: </span>2010-04-01</li><li><span>连载开始: </span>2009-10-15(2009年Vol.1)</li><li><span>连载结束: </span>2014-03-01(2014年Vol.14)</li>","collection":{"collect":1,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"已完结","count":1},{"name":"少女","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":9110,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ae/1d/9110_prsn_e6E63.jpg","name":"キリシマソウ","desc":"作者"},{"id":19306,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1c/1f/19306_prsn_x413b.jpg","name":"角川","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7611,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6d/b5/7611_prsn_9285i.jpg","name":"台湾尖端","desc":"出版社"},{"id":1581,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/51/e4/1581_prsn_U09wy.jpg","name":"enterbrain","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8586,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/02/75/8586_prsn_rYwd9.jpg","name":"comic B's-LOG キュン!","desc":"连载杂志"},{"id":10217,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ac/19/10217_prsn_0kbWc.jpg","name":"B's-LOG COMIC","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":193676,"name":"忍びよる恋はくせもの (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/f8/d5/193676_jp.jpg"},{"id":193673,"name":"忍びよる恋はくせもの (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/87/70/193673_jp.jpg"},{"id":193674,"name":"忍びよる恋はくせもの (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/73/81/193674_jp.jpg"},{"id":193675,"name":"忍びよる恋はくせもの (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/38/2e/193675_jp.jpg"},{"